headline: A Closer Look at Lululemon (LULU) Valuation After Analyst Upgrade and Growth Reset Plans
summary: Lululemon athletica (LULU) stock jumped after a key analyst upgrade suggested earlier concerns were already priced in. Company leaders also acknowledged lagging U.S. sales and outlined plans to bring more newness to their lineup. See our latest analysis for lululemon athletica. Lululemon’s recent analyst upgrade and acknowledgment of stale U.S. sales comes on the heels of a dramatic stretch for the stock, with a year-to-date share price return of -52.11% and a bruising 1-year total...
